register.text:
--- ID function Unit:GetID() return self.id end
--- ID function Unit:GetSymbolicID() return self:GetID() end
--- function Unit:SetParent(transform) self.actor:SetParent(transform) end
--- function Unit:SetPosition(position) self.position = position self.actor:SetPosition(position + Unit.POSITION_OFFSET) end
--- function Unit:LookDirection(direction) end
--- function Unit:LookAt(position) end
--- function Unit:GetPosition() return self.position end
--- Transform function Unit:GetTransform() return self.actor.ActorTransform end
--- function Unit:SetScale(scale) self.actor:SetScale(scale) end
--- function Unit:SetActive(active) self.actor:SetActive(active) end
--- function Unit:PlayAnimation(name) self.actor:PlayAnimation(name) end
--- function Unit:Destroy() ActorMgr.DestroyActor(self.id) end
-- Actor local actor = ActorMgr.CreateActor(id, assetPath) unit.actor = actor
